# Commits listed here are skipped by `git blame`, conventionally bulk
# formatting / rename commits whose churn would otherwise mask the
# original content author.
#
# Local setup (one-time per checkout):
#     git config blame.ignoreRevsFile .git-blame-ignore-revs
#
# GitHub honors this file automatically -- no setup needed there.
#
# Per-commit format: one full SHA per line, optionally followed by a
# `# comment` describing the commit. Blank lines and `#` comments are
# ignored.
#
